The paper proposes a deep learning model for simulating a dynamical system with unknown parameters, which involves statistical inference and recurrent neural networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), systems and control (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
